author: philip
msg: mod_dav_svn should not raise an error on POST requests outside a
Subversion location as these are not directed at Subversion.
(dav_svn__handler): Only process requests that are within a Subversion

author: stsp
msg: (close_file): In the case where symlink becomes a tree-conflict victim,
the nature of the conflict is already known, so replace the call to
check_tree_conflict() with a direct call to create_tree_conflict(),
as suggested by a comment (and remove said comment).
